extends layout

block content
  .main.container.text-xs-center
    h1.display-3 DigitalMe
    br
    h6 Welcome to DigitalMe, a place where you can share your thoughts, ideas and experiences.
    br
    h6 Registration is super easy and straight forward! Thanks to our implentation of Google+ API and Facebook for Developers, we've managed to implement a seamless and easy way to create an account!
